---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="mx-auto flex min-h-screen max-w-3xl flex-col justify-center gap-6 px-6 py-24">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium tracking-widest text-blue-600 uppercase">
      LeadGenLab · 리모델링
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-balance sm:text-5xl">
      AI 가시성 최적화(AVO)로 브랜드를 AI 추천 구조 안에 배치합니다.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
      새 디자인은 디자인 파이프라인으로 구축 예정. 콘텐츠 소스는
      <code class="rounded bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">docs/source-content.md</code>.
      셋업·작업 규칙은 <code class="rounded bg-gray-100 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">CLAUDE.md</code> 참조.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 pt-2">
      <a
        href="https://open.kakao.com/me/leadgenlab"
        class="rounded-lg bg-blue-600 px-5 py-3 font-medium text-white transition hover:bg-blue-700"
      >
        AI 가시성 무료 진단 요청
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://featpaper.com/l/fUgg4aBz"
        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-300 px-5 py-3 font-medium text-gray-900 transition hover:bg-gray-50"
      >
        회사소개서 보기
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
